## Layout Utilities

### Flexbox

```html
<!-- Horizontal layout -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
  <div>Item 1</div>
  <div>Item 2</div>
  <div>Item 3</div>
</div>

<!-- Vertical layout -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
  <div>Item 1</div>
  <div>Item 2</div>
  <div>Item 3</div>
</div>

<!-- Centered content -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-center h-screen">
  <div>Centered Content</div>
</div>

<!-- Space between items -->
<div class="flex justify-between">
  <div>Left</div>
  <div>Right</div>
</div>

<!-- Wrap items -->
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
  <div>Item 1</div>
  <div>Item 2</div>
  <div>Item 3</div>
</div>
```

### Grid

```html
<!-- 3-column grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <div>Column 1</div>
  <div>Column 2</div>
  <div>Column 3</div>
</div>

<!-- Responsive grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <div>Item 1</div>
  <div>Item 2</div>
  <div>Item 3</div>
</div>

<!-- Grid with different column spans -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
  <div class="col-span-3">Wide column</div>
  <div class="col-span-1">Narrow column</div>
</div>
```

### Spacing

```html
<!-- Margin -->
<div class="m-4">Margin all sides</div>
<div class="mt-4">Margin top</div>
<div class="mx-auto">Margin horizontal center</div>

<!-- Padding -->
<div class="p-6">Padding all sides</div>
<div class="px-4 py-2">Padding horizontal & vertical</div>

<!-- Space between children -->
<div class="space-y-4">
  <div>Item 1</div>
  <div>Item 2</div>
  <div>Item 3</div>
</div>

<div class="space-x-2">
  <span>Item 1</span>
  <span>Item 2</span>
  <span>Item 3</span>
</div>
```

